      "role": "user",
      "content": "But the \"Neutral-Match\" system is specifically designed to ignore those \"natural inclinations\" to ensure we don't violate the law. If we implement it, we won't be tailoring matches based on those \"similar characteristics\" you mentioned. Do you think switching to a system that ignores those profiles will actually make our clients unhappy?",
